===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A form of [[communication]] using [[word]]s either spoken or gestured with the hands and structured with [[grammar]], often with a writing [[system]].
#: {{usex|lang=en|the English '''language'''; &nbsp; sign '''language'''}}
