|title=[http://books.google.com/books?id=KnArAAAAMAAJ The History of the Caliph Vathek]
|passage=No '''language''' could express his rage and despair.}}
# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} The ability to communicate using words.
#: {{usex|lang=en|the gift of '''language'''}}
# {{context|countable|or|uncountable|lang=en}} Nonverbal communication.
#: {{usex|lang=en|body '''language'''}}
# {{context|computing|countable|lang=en}} A [[computer language]].
# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} The [[vocabulary]] and [[usage]] used in a particular [[specialist]] field.
